</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idbc559767-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective at close of <date date="1978-09-30">Sept. 30, 1978</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/95/478/s504">section 504 of Pub. L. 95–478</ref>, set out as an Effective Date of 1978 Amendment note under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s3001">section 3001 of this title</ref>.</p>
